data.text: …Jeez, even in your dreams you're still performing?
data.name: Narita Taishin

data.text:
Hey you two, it seems that dessert is being served… hmm? As 
expected, it seems as though Ticket has run out of energy.
data.name: Biwa Hayahide

data.text:
I'll go and get us 3 servings of cake. 
Taishin, keep an eye on Ticket.
data.name: Biwa Hayahide

data.text:
Yeah, yeah… Jeez, you're like a little kid, 
going full force until the very end, then running 
out of energy and falling asleep.
data.name: Narita Taishin

data.text:
Uwah!? Wai- Hey…!! 
Ah, jeez… she's not waking up…!!
data.name: Narita Taishin

data.text:
Ohh? The young ones sighed in sync… 
Still on cloud nine or somethin'?
data.name: Nice Nature

data.text:
Yes… To get to sing together with you, Teio-san, and 
Rudolf-san…! It still doesn't feel real!
data.name: Kitasan Black

data.text:
More importantly, it was so much fun! 
Again… I'd love to be able to experience that again…!!
data.name: Satono Diamond

data.text:
Woa- They… They're too pure! 
Although I guess I knew that already.
data.name: Nice Nature

data.text:
But yeah… You can experience that as many times as you want. As 
long as you continue to run with all you've got… doncha think?
data.name: Nice Nature

data.text:
Eh!? Nature is going to sing with Satono and the others again!? 
No fair! No fair!! I wanna sing too!!
data.name: Twin Turbo

data.text:
I agree… After all, we've been 
giving it our all as well.
data.name: Ikuno Dictus

data.text:
Ahaha! You're right!! 
Then I guess it's our time to strike!
data.name: Mejiro Palmer

data.text:
Uwah!? What's with you girls all of a sudden…? 
Wa-Wai-Wait! That hurts! Gueh…!
data.name: Nice Nature
